ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtClerkSOL = solar legion clerk's jumpskirt
    .desc = A formal jumpskirt with Solar Legion colorations. Worn by members of the Bureaucratic department.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtChiefEngineerSOL = solar legion chief engineer's jumpskirt
    .desc = It's a high visibility jumpskirt given to those engineers insane enough to achieve the rank of Chief Engineer within the Solar Legion.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtChiefEngineerTurtleSOL = solar legion chief engineer's turtleneck skirt
    .desc = An orange turtleneck designed specifically for work in conditions of the Solar Legion engineering department.
