ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtCmoTurtleSOL = solar legion medical director's turtleneck skirt
    .desc = It's a blue turtleneck with Solar Legion colorations. The silver trims denote the wearer as the head of a Solar Legion medical department.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtHosSOL = solar legion chief of police's jumpskirt
    .desc = A black turtleneck designed for a solar legion police chief. Features solar legion colors and silver badges to denote their rank and allegiance.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtQuartermasterTurtleneckSOL = solar legion quartermaster's turtleneck skirt
    .desc = It's a brown turtleneck skirt with Solar Legion colorations. The silver trims denote the wearer as the head of a Solar Legion cargo department.
ent-ClothingUniformJumpskirtRndSOL = solar legion research director's jumpskirt
